## Scan Execution Checklist

| Recipe | Hits |
|--------|------|
| `.ToLower()/.ToUpper()` | 2 (L97, L103) |
| `.All()/.Any()` on string | 2 (L93, L101) |
| `params` array | 1 (L213) |
| LINQ `.Select/.Cast/.Aggregate` | 3 sites (L86-89, L171, L214) |
| `.Replace(` | 1 (L187) |
| `.Contains(string)` w/o StringComparison | 0 (char overloads — OK) |
| Unsealed leaf classes | 3 of 3 (L226, L232, L237) |
| `sealed class` | 0 |
